f66ee3b817856ad7a45723c656836f7097419ac0942544aaa04d646bd45480c07615e5a2e2a2987347dd6907fcd25ee9b0ac84bfdc6bbe8cdff919a99484827b  add-smartcard-disable-option.patch
"
